        "description": "Creates a new sleep log entry for the user.\n\nRequired header:\n\n- `X-User-Id` : UUID format (e.g. c9061dc2-7e56-450e-99dd-a1b06280eb8b)\n    \n\nRequest body fields:\n\n- `logDate`: Sleep log date. Format YYYY-MM-DD (e.g., \"2026-04-12\" )\n    \n- `bedTime`: Go to bed time. Format **`YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ`** (e.g., \"2026-04-09T18:00:00Z\")\n    \n- `wakeTime`: Wake up time. Format **`YYYY-MM-DDTHH:mm:ssZ`** \"2026-04-10T07:00:00Z\"\n    \n- `mood`: \"GOOD\", \"OK\", \"BAD\"\n    \n\nReponse fields:\n\n- `id`: Id of the sleep log\n    \n- `logDate`\n    \n- `bedTime`\n    \n- `wakeTime`\n    \n- `mood`\n    \n- `totalDurationSeconds`: Total sleep duration in seconds"
      },
